b_{n}\geq b_{n+1}
\frac{\sum_{i=1}^{n}{a_i}}{n}\geq \frac{\sum_{i=1}^{n+1}{a_i}}{n+1}
n\sum_{i=1}^{n}{a_i}+\sum_{i=1}^{n}{a_i}\geq n\sum_{i=1}^{n}{a_i}+na_{n+1}
\sum_{i=1}^{n}{a_i}\geq na_{n+1}
